{"tid":2387680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最後我選擇左唔移民 留守香港","createTime":"2021-01-30T13:30:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T16:10:48.000Z","uid":302,"like":23,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"bc9407f7fbd81dea767952b14b2c73d438d84e54","tid":2387680,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T13:30:11.000Z","msg":"其實而家已經係最後一刻既人生交叉點 <br />\n<br />\n去 還是 留<br />\n<br />\n我選擇 留<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多人話 有能力既就應該走 <br />\n<br />\n我反而認為<br />\n<br />\n係有能力先好選擇留低 <br />\n<br />\n冇能力去接受即將被全面打壓<br />\n<br />\n冇能力去接受香港即將全面赤化既人<br />\n<br />\n就應該離開<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我已經有晒心理準備留低係度<br />\n<br />\n留低後我會表面選擇做順民<br />\n<br />\n背後裝備自己 然後就係等一個機會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我相信留低既人 都會一齊 <br />\n<br />\n一齊等個一刻既來臨"},{"pid":"4d12d7b1ff897f42490453c43180494b92fc5b05","tid":2387680,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T13:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511a6ad5e381ad74790c3e04a37bca7cbc667cb2","tid":2387680,"uid":146030,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T13:31:53.000Z","msg":"你一定會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3845ee89768b79831eab9acb6d0541165dc443","tid":2387680,"uid":302,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"511a6ad5e381ad74790c3e04a37bca7cbc667cb2","tid":2387680,"uid":146030,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T13:31:53.000Z","msg":"你一定會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T13:32:57.000Z","msg":"可能36歲後會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8d6f8a81ecbd3b39e7c806b526c7d58935f354","tid":2387680,"uid":136416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T13:33:00.000Z","msg":"一齊愛國愛黨<br />\n鬥紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3d5ec7513b80818b858f4fbdb43bd426c569c8"